  <div class="large-4 small-4 xsmall-4 columns">        <a href="/2018/08/structural-change-disinflation-and-amazonisation"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="https://www.newstatesman.com/sites/default/files/styles/trending_264_198/public/blogs_2018/08/amazon.jpg?itok=wf1wWTzy" alt="" /></a>  </div>  
          <div class="large-8 small-8 xsmall-8 columns"><h5> <a href="/2018/08/structural-change-disinflation-and-amazonisation">Structural change, disinflation and “Amazonisation”</a></h5><div class="article-author">By Janus Henderson</div>
</div>    
          
<div class="sponsored-hover-2017">
	<div class="large-4 small-4 xsmall-4 columns">       
	  <a href="/2018/08/structural-change-disinflation-and-amazonisation"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="https://www.newstatesman.com/sites/default/files/styles/trending_264_198/public/blogs_2018/08/amazon.jpg?itok=wf1wWTzy" alt="" /></a>
	 
	 </div>  
	<div class="large-8 small-8 xsmall-8 columns"><h5> <a href="/spotlight/fintech/2018/04/evolving-education"><a href="/2018/08/structural-change-disinflation-and-amazonisation">Structural change, disinflation and “Amazonisation”</a></a></h5>
		<div class="article-author">By  Janus Henderson  </div>
	</div>    
	<div class="large-8 small-8 xsmall-8 columns"> <p> <p>
